      "summary": "Read-only learning exercise that runs the model-free dump tool on two corpus documents and traces a page through the pipeline by inspecting the ast/enriched/chunks artifacts, calibrating the reader's mental model before any code changes.",
      "tags": ["documentation", "exercise", "learning", "pipeline", "tracing"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "Walkthrough-style exercise with a hidden answer key in a <details> block; references dump.py and enrichment internals (_SECTION_RULES, _write_to_field)."
    },
    {
      "id": "document:docs/learn/exercises/02-add-a-section-keyword.md",
