      "name": "02-add-a-section-keyword.md",
      "filePath": "docs/learn/exercises/02-add-a-section-keyword.md",
      "summary": "Hands-on exercise to add an 'Observability' keyword to enrichment's _SECTION_RULES so such headings classify to a real SectionType, while respecting rule order and substring-collision constraints, and to extend the parametrized classification test.",
      "tags": ["documentation", "exercise", "learning", "enrichment", "classification"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "document:docs/learn/exercises/03-parametrize-header-norm.md",
