      "summary": "Exercise to add a search_default_results setting to PipelineConfig, teaching the dual-branch trap where config.py defines the class twice (pydantic-settings v2 and a v1 fallback) and both branches must stay in sync.",
      "tags": ["documentation", "exercise", "learning", "configuration", "pydantic"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "document:docs/learn/exercises/05-extend-an-entity-pattern.md",
