      "name": "05-extend-an-entity-pattern.md",
      "filePath": "docs/learn/exercises/05-extend-an-entity-pattern.md",
      "summary": "Exercise to extend enrichment's _SERVICE_PATTERN regex with Orchestrator/Dispatcher suffixes, test it, then re-dump a real corpus doc to measure the (empty) blast radius — teaching the verify-before/verify-after discipline.",
      "tags": ["documentation", "exercise", "learning", "enrichment", "entity-extraction"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
